    "A variety of artificial intelligence models are employed to provide conversational responses to inquiries based on extensive text data.",
    "ChatGPT is designed to remember both user input and its own responses within a conversation, allowing it to build upon previous responses as new inquiries are received (4).",
    "The effectiveness of ChatGPT has been considered in several healthcare domains, including its capacity to diagnose dental problems.",
    "It has been demonstrated that it provides accurate differential diagnoses in a substantial number of cases, compared favorably with the diagnostic abilities of healthcare professionals (5).",
    "In the realm of dentistry, research on ChatGPT's effectiveness remains limited."
